{"tid":2104603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"既然對香港有信心 大家請投鄺俊宇一票幫鄺神上車供樓","createTime":"2020-07-12T05:50:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T15:48:56.000Z","uid":13745,"like":13,"dislike":119,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"d5e13dc92f2f4066f2a76bbf3dff7d72df6959a7","tid":2104603,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T05:50:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/6736866-鄺俊宇擁千萬物業-惹未申報疑雲\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F6736866-%E9%84%BA%E4%BF%8A%E5%AE%87%E6%93%81%E5%8D%83%E8%90%AC%E7%89%A9%E6%A5%AD-%E6%83%B9%E6%9C%AA%E7%94%B3%E5%A0%B1%E7%96%91%E9%9B%B2&d=GdzNT1%2FdEV%2FiwqmWSoLNnr3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=2ee49db3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/6736866-鄺俊宇擁千萬物業-惹未申報疑雲</a><br />\n<br />\n最新一期《東周刊》報道，出身公屋的民主黨立法會議員鄺俊宇，原來早於一八年就斥資一千零三十多萬元，購入大角嘴「利奧坊．凱岸」一個實用面積四百一十七平方呎單位的樓花，平均呎價約二萬四千七百元，並於今年四月正式成為千萬豪宅業主。<br />\n<br />\n鄺俊宇做千萬業主惹來兩大質疑，包括有指他遲遲未按《議事規則》申報，涉嫌違規，以及他身為區議會和立法會「雙料議員」，月入十多萬元，早已達公屋富戶標準，究竟是否仍保留公屋戶籍？<br />\n<br />\n鄺俊宇日前向傳媒解釋，為方便往返立法會，一八年在大角嘴購入一個單位，在此之前已刪除在天水圍公屋的戶籍。他又指，新居是他唯一及主要並經常自住的居所，秘書處向他確認毋須向立法會申報，做法無違反《議事規則》。"},{"pid":"c29b6449ac35ed52b6669661e44abe9ffd2c9f89","tid":2104603,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T05:51:53.000Z","msg":"【用銀包投票】民主黨立法會議員鄺俊宇承認近日遷入自購新居<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.speakout.hk/港人花生/59138/-用銀包投票-民主黨立法會議員鄺俊宇承認近日遷入自購新居#selected\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.speakout.hk%2F%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%8A%B1%E7%94%9F%2F59138%2F-%E7%94%A8%E9%8A%80%E5%8C%85%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8-%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E9%BB%A8%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E9%84%BA%E4%BF%8A%E5%AE%87%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D%E8%BF%91%E6%97%A5%E9%81%B7%E5%85%A5%E8%87%AA%E8%B3%BC%E6%96%B0%E5%B1%85%23selected&d=GdzNT1%2FdEV%2FiwqmWSoLNnr3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=18d47324\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.speakout.hk/港人花生/59138/-用銀包投票-民主黨立法會議員鄺俊宇承認近日遷入自購新居#selected</a><br />\n<br />\n民主黨立法會議員鄺俊宇近期搬至自購的新居。據報，鄺購入的屋苑為位於大角咀、樓齡約兩年的私樓「利奧坊‧凱岸」，單位417呎單位，估值逾1,100萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n豪花1,100萬購入單位，足證鄺俊宇對香港前途充滿信心。多謝鄺俊宇向香港投下信心一票。"},{"pid":"63c983d483e11531ea367b7b55652394caa77017","tid":2104603,"uid":344625,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T05:53:02.000Z","msg":"好酸"},{"pid":"5871d48453400dde4e03e92b85dab86c26b67664","tid":2104603,"uid":13745,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T05:53:09.000Z","msg":"【香港已死?】<br />\n前特首梁振英<br />\n在港台節目談國安法<br />\n提及鄺俊宇千萬置業<br />\n鄺俊宇日前透露<br />\n單位是兩年前買入<br />\n並已刪除天水圍的公屋戶籍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/2020-07-12-13-11-38c0e4VeUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2F2020-07-12-13-11-38c0e4VeUF.jpg&h=8d27e69e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"60d013a8d73a9dd08cd813abcb9913061034df39","tid":2104603,"uid":289946,"like":70,"dislike":1,"score":69,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T05:54:03.000Z","msg":"出糧儲錢上車都要批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc36715375cd12cea401431778f73af321186340","tid":2104603,"uid":276865,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T05:54:24.000Z","msg":"住公屋又人血, 自己買樓又人血<br />\n屌你老母咩"},{"pid":"9e101e3a51a8f116113c6679cd33c54fb12cb335","tid":2104603,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"63c983d483e11531ea367b7b55652394caa77017","tid":2104603,"uid":344625,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T05:53:02.000Z","msg":"好酸"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T05:54:27.000Z","msg":"又話香港已死 一國兩制玩完？<br />\n鄺神重唔快啲掟貨"},{"pid":"29cc5655c40261e8a67697e2163b1576fbbc8e6e","tid":2104603,"uid":13745,"like":3,"dislike":26,"score":-23,"quote":{"pid":"60d013a8d73a9dd08cd813abcb9913061034df39","tid":2104603,"uid":289946,"like":70,"dislike":1,"score":69,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-